Detailed Description template<bool External_Load_Access = false, typename Size_Type = std::size_t>class __gnu_pbds::hash_load_check_resize_trigger< External_Load_Access, Size_Type >
A resize trigger policy based on a load check. It keeps the load factor between some load factors load_min and load_max.
